kboards. <#/>And in the 37 poorest countries in the world, spending per head on schools has declined by 25 per cent in the last decade while in two out of every three}{\b\fs24\lang2057  }{\fs24\lang2057 countries spending per student}{\b\fs24\lang2057  }{
\fs24\lang2057 is lower now than it}{\b\fs24\lang2057  }{\fs24\lang2057 was in 1980 according to United Nations sources.
