\par }\pard\plain \qj\nowidctlpar\adjustright \fs20\lang1031 {<#/>}{\fs24\lang2057 A Deputy Director of Unicef, Dr Richard Jolly, cautions that investment in human capital in the form of
 nutrition, basic education and health cannot be postponed. <#/>"It either takes place at an appropriate age when the need is present or it does not. <#/>For the young, there is no second chance, the director, who is an economist says.
